{"tid":2450344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.28上環暴動案  警員看片段後稱不同特徵人士為同一被告","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T11:38:27.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac44a51f86a621d4aef2f7a01ef99263a0ea72f","tid":2450344,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:13:15.000Z","msg":"前年7⽉28⽇，⽰威者與警⽅在上環爆發激烈衝突，當中23人被控暴動的案件今日續審。主控官資深大律師郭棟明花近全日播放當天新聞片段，讓拘捕第五被告陳（24歲）的偵緝警員翻看案發前的片段，看看是否有被告身影。<span class=\"red\">警員及後在多段片段均指出「見到第五被告」，主控並將片段截圖，讓警員圈出他聲稱是「第五被告」的黑衫人，但事實上警員所指稱的「第五被告」特徵並不一致。</span><br />\n<br />\n背囊、防具、雨傘、手套時有時無<br />\n<br />\n偵緝警員14064林建邦承認，<span class=\"red\">昨日</span>庭上播放的拘捕及制服第五被告的片段中，<span class=\"red\">被告沒有孭住背囊</span>，當時手上亦沒有白手套、防毒面具、護目鏡、背囊及雨傘；但<span class=\"gold\">今日播片他認出的那個「第五被告」則有孭住背囊等其他特徵</span>。"},{"pid":"f0ed9c5c5f8ca7c2e7443593bbac7df7e4f43c9e","tid":2450344,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/KK23ZGGF3NBHHPR2MOQWRAMMRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FKK23ZGGF3NBHHPR2MOQWRAMMRU%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=de869ecb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FKK23ZGGF3NBHHPR2MOQWRAMMRU%2F&h=cfaad534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/KK23ZGGF3NBHHPR2MOQWRAMMRU/</a>"},{"pid":"de47ebe8bd8f34530b9aa2923d896b786102bfda","tid":2450344,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d593807d25bd9c847f714e183f34c6f8b38cbf5","tid":2450344,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"手足黎<br />\n認唔人=告唔入"},{"pid":"21453ee038684526f92950e93c7dbf72fbfa2878","tid":2450344,"uid":27122,"like":0,"